lead_paragraph: A sluggish start to Game Three cost the Golden State Warriors a chance to move within a win of a second consecutive NBA title and could ultimately prove to be the turning point in their Finals series against the Cleveland Cavaliers.

headline.print_headline: Slow-Starting Warriors Rue Chance to Deliver Decisive Blow
